---
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1><span>Vellaveto</span> &mdash; Runtime Security for AI Agents</h1>
    <p class="tagline">The MCP firewall that intercepts, evaluates, and enforces policy on every AI agent tool call.</p>
    <p class="compliance">EU AI Act + NIS2 + DORA compliant</p>
    <div class="install" id="install">
      <span class="label">Quick start</span>
      <code>docker run -p 3000:3000 ghcr.io/paolovella/vellaveto:latest</code>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero{padding:9rem 0 5rem;text-align:center}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:800;
    line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .hero h1 span{background:var(--grad);-webkit-background-clip:text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
  .tagline{font-size:1.125rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .compliance{font-size:.95rem;color:var(--teal);font-weight:600;
    margin-bottom:2.5rem}
  .install{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:.5rem;padding:1rem 1.25rem;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.875rem;overflow-x:auto}
  .install code{white-space:nowrap;color:var(--accent)}
  .label{color:var(--muted);font-size:.75rem;font-family:var(--sans);flex-shrink:0}
  @media(max-width:600px){
    .hero{padding:7rem 0 3.5rem}
    .hero h1{font-size:1.75rem}
    .install{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}
  }
</style>
